Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.95,1:28:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}南北分治的局面吗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}separate governments on both sides of the Yangtze?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.03,1:28:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}换做是你 你会接受吗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Would you accept if it were you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.00,1:29:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这要看美国和苏联的态度 还有{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}That'd depend on the US and the USSR...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.96,1:29:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}没那么复杂 谁的态度也不用看{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Don't make it so complicated. It doesn't matter what anyone thinks{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.09,1:29:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}南北朝可以出现在过去{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}China was split into north and south in the past{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.05,1:29:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}但绝不会出现在今天{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}but not today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.97,1:29:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}谁敢当这个千古的罪人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Who would want to be blamed for it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.10,1:29:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这胆量我没有{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Definitely not me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.06,1:29:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}张澜先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Mr. Zhang Lan{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.02,1:29:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}您认为此时此刻{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Right now, in your opinion,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.94,1:29:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}中共会接受政府的求和声明吗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}will the CPC accept the Government's plea for peace?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.11,1:29:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}绝无可能{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.11,1:29:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}为什么会是这样{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Why is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.03,1:29:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}蒋介石不放弃所谓宪法{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}If Chiang never gives up his so-called constitution,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.99,1:29:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}不要说共产党不会认{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}The CPC will not recognize it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.91,1:29:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}人民也不会认{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}and neither will the people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.12,1:29:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}您对毛泽东周恩来很了解{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}You know Mao Zedong and Zhou Enlai very well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.08,1:29:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}他们这些人究竟是本土的革命家{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Are they local revolutionaries{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.08,1:29:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}还是共产国际情报局在中国的代理人呢{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}or mere agents working for international communist intelligence bureau?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.96,1:29:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这个时候 这还算是个问题吗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}What kind of question is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.09,1:29:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}是问题 我想知道您的态度{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I want to know your view.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.97,1:29:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}我的态度是 中共顺应了民意{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}My view is that the CPC catered for the people{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.02,1:30:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}所以才有今天的成就{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}which explains their achievements today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.98,1:30:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}成就{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Achievements?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.90,1:30:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}对 成就{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Yes, achievements.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.94,1:30:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}宜生兄大鉴{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Dear Zuoyi{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.11,1:30:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}相处多年 彼此深知{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}You and I have come a long way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.12,1:30:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}兄今厄于形势 自作主张{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Given the circumstances, you took matters into your own hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.08,1:30:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}无可奈何 弟惟求一事{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}There's nothing I can do about that, but I have one request.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.04,1:30:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}明日起 派飞机抵平{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I will send planes to Beiping tomorrow{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.00,1:30:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}运走十三军少校以上军宫{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}to airlift officers of the 13th Army ranked Major or above{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.92,1:30:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}及必要武器{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}and essential weaponry{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.96,1:30:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}望念多年契好 予以协肋{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}On account of our long standing friendship, please help me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.97,1:30:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}蒋中正{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Chiang Chung-cheng.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.13,1:31:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}北平沦陷 傅作义投降{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Beiping fell Fu Zuoyi surrendered.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.09,1:31:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}共军又逼近长江 逼近南京{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}The CPC is moving in on the Yangtze and Nanjing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.05,1:31:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}我发出求和声明{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}With regards to my plea for peace,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.02,1:31:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}中共虽然接受了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}the CPC accepted it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.06,1:31:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}却提出八项极端苛刻之条件{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}but raised 8 very harsh conditions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.90,1:31:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}夫人 只有您出面代表政府{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Madame, if you speak on behalf of the Government,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.94,1:31:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}毛周二人才可能相信我李宗仁{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Mao and Zhou may trust me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.12,1:31:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}代总统 你是知道的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}As you know, Mr. Acting President,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.95,1:31:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}自内战重开之时 我就不问政事了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I washed my hands in politics since the onset of the civil war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.00,1:31:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}前几天报纸传谣说要我出山{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}There are rumors in the newspapers about me coming out of retirement.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.00,1:31:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}基金会还正式出面辟谣{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}The Trust had to issue a denial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.05,1:31:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}夫人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Madame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.97,1:32:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}国民党乃中山先生所创建{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Dr. Sun founded the KMT.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.10,1:32:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}您总不能眼睁睁的看着它{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}You can't sit back and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.94,1:32:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}万劫不复{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}watch it go to ruin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.04,1:32:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}别忘了 你虽然当了代总统{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Don't forget, you may be the Acting President,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.17,1:32:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}但蒋介石还是国民党的总裁{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}but Chiang Kai-shek is still the Party Chairman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.98,1:32:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}看来 李代总统的日子不好过呀{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Looks like the Acting President is having a hard time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.03,1:33:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}是啊 蒋介石名义上退位{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Chiang stepped down in name only{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.12,1:33:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}可依旧操纵着背后的一切{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}He still has control of everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.95,1:33:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}李宗仁手上没有足够的权力{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Li Zongren does not have enough authority.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.16,1:33:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}实际上是个傀儡{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}He's only a puppet{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.12,1:33:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这样的谈判是不会有结果的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Nothing will come out of the negotiation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.13,1:33:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}怪不得您不肯答应李代总统{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}No wonder you turned him down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.01,1:33:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}我只是不愿意去北平{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I don't want to go to Beiping{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.97,1:33:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}中山先生病逝在那里 伤心之地啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}because Dr. Sun died there. Too many memories.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.07,1:33:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}表老 您是同盟会的前辈{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Master Zhang, you're a veteran of the United League{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.16,1:33:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}朱德的老师{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}and Zhu De's mentor{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.12,1:33:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}周恩来和董必武都很佩服您的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Zhou Enlai and Dong Biwu have great respect for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.16,1:33:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}代总统发表了和谈声明{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}The Acting President issued a declaration for peace negotiation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.16,1:33:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这居中调停之重任就非您老莫属了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}You're the most suitable person to mediate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.96,1:33:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}中共既然提出了八项条件{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}If the CPC brought up 8 conditions,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.05,1:34:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}你们谈就是了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}go ahead and talk to them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.18,1:34:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}毛泽东若真肯谈的话{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}If Mao wants to talk,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.14,1:34:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}怎么会提出这么苛刻的条件{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}he wouldn't raise these harsh conditions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.97,1:34:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}谈判谈判 总要有得谈才是{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}There should be room to negotiate in a negotiation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.06,1:34:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}所以李代总统让我去跟中共讨价还价{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}That's why the Acting President sent me to haggle with them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.99,1:34:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}是居中调停{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}To mediate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.95,1:34:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}你们知道 政府已经取缔了民盟{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}As you know, the Government clamped down on the CDL.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.03,1:34:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}如今民盟是个非法组织{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}It is now an illegal organization{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.00,1:34:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}我与中共是一党喽{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I'm now in the same party as the Communists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.00,1:34:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}表老 您不要生气{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Please don't be upset, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.13,1:34:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}那是蒋先生的命令{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Mr Chiang issued that order,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.05,1:34:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}跟代总统不相干的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}not the Acting President.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.09,1:34:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}我张澜站在革命一边{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I side with the revolutionary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.14,1:34:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}还能替敌人讨价还价吗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}I won't haggle for the enemy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.18,1:34:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}表老{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.01,1:34:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}送客{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}See them out{\r}
