Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.27,1:41:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}早啊 当班啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Morning, you're on duty?{\r}
