Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.26,1:43:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}成俊同志 你是县委书记{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Chengjun, you're the county committee secretary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.09,1:43:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这可不行{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}This can't go on.{\r}
