Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.23,1:43:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}要革他们的命{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}and we should punish them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.31,1:43:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}吓得这些商人买卖全不敢做了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}They're so scared no one is open for business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.19,1:43:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这不是个小问题{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}This is not a small matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.32,1:43:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}闹革命 我们天下第一{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Revolution is our forte{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.20,1:43:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}搞经济 我们可比不了他们{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}but not economics.{\r}
