Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.13,1:43:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}生产关系的改变不是过家家{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Production must be handled with care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.30,1:43:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}不能胡来 一旦搞出了问题{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}If anything goes wrong,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.09,1:43:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}那比在战场上打了败仗还糟糕{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}it'll be worse than losing a battle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.14,1:43:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}要有自知之明{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}We must know our limits{\r}
