Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.19,1:43:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}政治协商 协商的对象就是{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}The gist of political consultation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.15,1:44:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}资产阶级政党和民主人士{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}involves capitalists and democracy activists.{\r}
