Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.15,1:44:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这个问题必须明确 搞垮了人家{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}We must be very clear on this: If we destroy them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.32,1:44:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}自己又不懂得经营生产{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}and we can't run production on our own,{\r}
