Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.33,1:44:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这不是砸自己饭碗么{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}We'll be smashing our own rice bowls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.21,1:44:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}这个饭碗我们刚刚端上 砸不得{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}We barely got our hands on them, don't smash them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.07,1:44:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}同志们 今天有两个要求{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Comrades, we ask two things of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.99,1:44:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}挺直腰板 声音洪亮 明白吗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Keep your backs straight and your voices up, understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.07,1:44:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典隶书简\fs20\bord0\shad0}听明白啦{\r}\N{\fs12\bord0\shad0}Yes.{\r}
